<body>
<main class="container">
    <section class="text-center">
        <h2>Simplify Your Invoicing. Grow Your Business.</h2>
        <p class="lead">Powerful invoicing software designed for small businesses, freelancers, and entrepreneurs. Focus on your work, not the paperwork.</p>
        <p>We are currently building a comprehensive invoicing solution that will streamline your billing process, manage clients and inventory, and provide valuable insights into your business finances.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h3 class="text-center">Key Benefits (Coming Soon)</h3>
        <div class="mt-6" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-around; text-align: center;">
            <div class="p-4" style="flex: 1;"> <h4>Save Time</h4>
                <p>Create and send professional invoices in minutes, not hours.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4" style="flex: 1;">
                <h4>Stay Organized</h4>
                <p>Keep all client and item details in one place.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4" style="flex: 1;">
                <h4>Get Paid Faster</h4>
                <p>Easy payment tracking and reminders.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h3 class="text-center">Features</h3>
        <div class="mt-6 features-section">
            <div class="mt-6" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-around; text-align: center;">
                <div class="p-4" style="flex: 1;"> <h4>Invoice Tracking</h4>
                    <p>You can see all of the invoices sent with their statuses like "paid", "partially paid", "cancelled" or "rejected".</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-around; text-align: center;">
                <div class="p-4" style="flex: 1;"> <h4>Invoice Drafts</h4>
                    <p>Save invoice as drafts for future or reference.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-around; text-align: center;">
                <div class="p-4" style="flex: 1;"> <h4>Invoice clone</h4>
                    <p>Start creating a new invoice based on existing ones.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-around; text-align: center;">
                <div class="p-4" style="flex: 1;"> <h4>Invoice clone</h4>
                    <p>Start creating a new invoice based on existing ones.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-around; text-align: center;">
                <div class="p-4" style="flex: 1;"> <h4>Dashboard</h4>
                    <p>Current open list, stats based on status (sent, partial, paid, cancelled, rejected etc.), stats based on age (old partial, old not paid).</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-around; text-align: center;">
                <div class="p-4" style="flex: 1;"> <h4>Customizable Notes/Memo</h4>
                    <p>Add messages for the client "Thank you for your business! Looking forward to serve you.", or set of Terms and conditions specific to the invoice or generic for business, or a memo for credits remaining or some debt or maybe reminder for payment date.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-around; text-align: center;">
                <div class="p-4" style="flex: 1;"> <h4>Professional branding on invoice</h4>
                    <p>Add your Business logo to indicate brand value on the invoice.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-around; text-align: center;">
                <div class="p-4" style="flex: 1;"> <h4>Custome Invoice Number</h4>
                    <a href="/plan-and-milestones.html#invoice-number-patterns">Your own invoice pattern. For project, product or year.</a>
                    <p>Match your existing numbering system. Or <a href="/plan-and-milestones.html#invoice-number-patterns">create one of your own</a>.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-around; text-align: center;">
                <div class="p-4" style="flex: 1;"> <h4>Add discount</h4>
                    <p>Apply a discount to the entire invoice or specific line items.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-around; text-align: center;">
                <div class="p-4" style="flex: 1;"> <h4>Basic Sales Tax</h4>
                    <p>You can apply a basic sales to the entire invoice.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section"> <h2>Be the First to Know!</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">Sign up for updates to follow our development progress and get notified when we launch.</p>
        <form action="#" method="post" class="mt-6 cta-form"> <input type="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
            <button type="submit">Get Updates</button>
        </form>
    </section>
</main>
